updated_at: "2026-07-06T22:11:13.026Z"
author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 300
acceptance_criteria: "Exemplar package builds+tests using only public SDK imports; exercises lifecycle, query, annotations, governance, schema customization; linked tests run in CI; referenced from SDK docs as the build-your-own-PM-tool guide"
